<paragraph id="8351A36FFFBEFFC3FF0EFB8AB744FBFB" blockId="7.[172,1230,1052,1143]" pageId="7" pageNumber="212">
Note. The species is known from Rodrigues Island. Although the copulatory organs of this species are not illustrated, figures of the habitus clearly indicate that it belongs to 
<taxonomicName id="44EED8ECFFBEFFC3FF43FBCAB523FBFA" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1804" box="[172,316,1116,1142]" class="Arachnida" family="Tetragnathidae" genus="Tetragnatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="7" pageNumber="212" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B19A7F7DFFBEFFC3FF43FBCAB523FBFA" box="[172,316,1116,1142]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="212">Tetragnatha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and therefore we suggest a new combination.
</paragraph>
